title: Wizard Of Legend MacOS
description:
Genre: Action, Adventure
Developer: Contingent99
Publisher: Contingent99
Language: English
Size: 328MB
Wizard of Legend is a no-nonsense, action-packed take on wizardry that emphasizes precise movements and smart comboing of spells in a rogue-like dungeon crawler that features over a hundred unique spells and relics!
STEAM PAGE

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
MINIMUM:
OS: Mac OS X 10.9 or later
Processor: Intel Core i3
Memory: 4 GB RAM
Graphics: OpenGL 2.0 Compatible
Storage: 1 GB available space
Additional Notes: Gamepad support for XInput devices
